  <brief_title>Serum DCAMKL1 Pre and Post Treatment in Patients With Pancreatic Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Expression Patterns of Stem Cell Marker Doublecortin and CaM Kinase-Like-1 (DCAMKL-1) in Human Pancreatic Adenocarcinoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
