  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators believe DCAMKL-1 is a stem cell tumor marker and is elevated in patients
      with pancreatic cancer. The investigators would like to analyze its expression pre and post
      treatment, to gauge the correlation between current pancreatic cancer therapies and the
      expression of DCAMKL-1
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
